high_descs: Turn left and head to the counter.
Pick up the knife by the blue plate.
Turn around and go the counter with the toaster.
Cut the potato in front of the toaster.
Look up towards the toaster.
Put the knife in front of the salt.
Look down towards the potato.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left, go towards the door, turn left and go to the fridge.
Put the slice of potato on the second shelf in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge and pick up the slice of potato.
Turn around and go to the recycling can.
Put the slice of potato in the recycling can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of potato in the recycling can.

high_descs: Turn left and head to the counter beside the sink
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn left then head to the stove counter on the left
Slice the potato on the counter
Move forward to the counter
Put the knife on the counter beside the potato
Step backward and face the potato
Pick up a slice potato on the counter
Turn left then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the slice potato
Turn left then head to the trash bin
Put the slice potato in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled slice potato in the trash bin

high_descs: Turn to the counter by the sink on your left.
Take the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the counter with the bread in front of you.
Slice the potato on the counter in front of you.
Face the counter in front of you.
Place the knife on the counter in front of you.
Face the potato on the counter in front of you.
Take a potato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the fridge on your left.
Place the potato slice in the fridge for a bit, then take it out and close the fridge.
Turn around and face the green can on your right.
Place the potato slice in the green can in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold potato slice in the green bin.
